        "summary": "Get Memory Log Stats",
        "description": "获取记忆日志统计信息\n\n返回格式:\n{\n    \"status\": \"success\",\n    \"data\": {\n        \"total_memories\": 150,\n        \"conversations\": 50,\n        \"observations\": 100,\n        \"today_count\": 20,\n        \"storage_size\": \"2.5 MB\"\n    }\n}",
